      "id": "id_1040",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 52,
      "y": 440,
      "width": 416,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "Mobile Guard — asaas_guard1\nLogin → Mobile UI (#asaasMobileApp)\n1. Log item: building/floor/spot + corridor photo\n2. Sticker photo (photo2) on physical item\n3. Return: collector name + signed paper photo\nLogout: PASSWORD required\nLanguages: EN / Sorani",
      "originalText": "Mobile Guard — asaas_guard1\nLogin → Mobile UI (#asaasMobileApp)\n1. Log item: building/floor/spot + corridor photo\n2. Sticker photo (photo2) on physical item\n3. Return: collector name + signed paper photo\nLogout: PASSWORD required\nLanguages: EN / Sorani",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "id_1039",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
