      "id": "id_1064",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 52,
      "y": 1000,
      "width": 896,
      "height": 160,
      "text": "API Actions (POST + token)\ngetAsaasItems — read all | addAsaasItem — create (any asaas token)\nupdateAsaasItem — sticker photo (asaas_guard1 ONLY)\nmarkAsaasReturned — close item (asaas_guard1 ONLY)\ndeleteAsaasItem / clearAsaasItems — no admin check, not in UI (SECURITY REVIEW)\nverifyPassword — mobile logout confirm",
      "originalText": "API Actions (POST + token)\ngetAsaasItems — read all | addAsaasItem — create (any asaas token)\nupdateAsaasItem — sticker photo (asaas_guard1 ONLY)\nmarkAsaasReturned — close item (asaas_guard1 ONLY)\ndeleteAsaasItem / clearAsaasItems — no admin check, not in UI (SECURITY REVIEW)\nverifyPassword — mobile logout confirm",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "id_1063",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
